{"tid":974731,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一則笑話-1😂😂😂","createTime":"2019-01-09T06:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T08:02:33.000Z","uid":101328,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c07a335948be683038e318fe2ab0e70081760ac3","tid":974731,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"昨晚我在路邊..<br />\n遇到一位身材姣好的辣妹～<br />\n<br />\n看她在那裡一直猛灌啤酒，<br />\n估計已經喝了快兩手了～<br />\n<br />\n具我觀察，應該是感情受創，<br />\n以致借酒消愁。<br />\n<br />\n我見機不可失！心想..<br />\n今晚有獵物該下手了～<br />\n<br />\n看她最後一瓶啤酒喝完要離開了，<br />\n她站都站不穩 又跌坐在地上....<br />\n<br />\n嘿...嘿嘿&hellip;我的機會來了～<br />\n<br />\n我走了過去說：<br />\n<br />\n「小姐.&hellip;不好意思<br />\n<br />\n那些空瓶子，可以給我資源回收嗎？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af50231be8a56e72e06b8edd8b462f725695b5bd","tid":974731,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:05:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0b4f0340bc6011113200a318edf7badb791b3380","tid":974731,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />pish"},{"pid":"9e6c8b54d410ed2af303a1af9534daba11c7e80e","tid":974731,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5Xhs3N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5Xhs3N.jpg&h=10261f7f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}